TLDR: This work created remote sensing image training patch samples in a novel and automatic way, then trained a deep learning convolutional neural network, named DescNet, to generate a robust feature descriptor for feature matching, and analyzed the advantages of the created training dataset Invar-Dataset and DescNet and gave the possible development of training deep descriptor network.},
  file = {D\:\\Documents\\Zotero\\storage\\IHQGH2SX\\Dong et al_2019_Local Deep Descriptor for Remote Sensing Image Feature Matching.pdf;I\:\\Disks\\OneDrive\\Bibliography\\Zotero\\Dong et al_2019_Local Deep Descriptor for Remote Sensing Image Feature Matching.pdf}
